org.mpxj.primavera.webservices

Class WebServicesProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mpxj.primavera.webservices.WebServicesProject

  • public class WebServicesProject
extends Object
    Represents a project exposed via the P6 Web Services API. Returned when projects in P6 are listed, and used when requesting a project export.
